thread.title: Coronation Street

author: Sheena McGinley
title: Coronation Street
text: Yikes. This isn't at all embarrassing, by the looks of things. As Sally makes last minute preparations for her wedding - who nobody turns up to if appearances are to be believed, she begs Tim to change his mind and marry her. Meanwhile, Carla is stunned when Aidan's dad Johnny and sister Kate burst into the factory demanding to see him. Mrs Connor has a right go at Aidan for lying about where he got his investment money from. Meanwhile, Tyrone's exhaustion leads to a mistake at work, and Craig is stunned when Caitlin turns up on the street.
